<p>
  <h2>Professional Background</h2></p>
  <p><b>Consultant (promoted from Analyst), Accenture (2011 – 2015)
Industries: Communication/Media, Utilities, Technology, Manufacturing, Oil/Gas, Financial Services, Federal</b></p>

<p>I spent five years at Accenture after joining upon graduating from the University of Texas at Austin as an Analyst. I was promoted from an Analyst to Consultant for pioneering processes that used raw data to forecast capacity needs for external supply chains to be used in sales and operations planning. My focus includes designing business processes, project management, business case development, supply chain planning and mergers an acquisition.</p>

