<p><b>Art of Business Chair, Business Council for the Arts: Leadership Arts Institute (2013 – 2014)</b></p>

<p>The Leadership Arts Institute is an annual program that teaches a curriculum to 60 selected participants “best practices” to future board leaders. I chaired the Art of Business series, which educated 75 nonprofit leaders on business practices to improve their organization. </p>



